snippet.title: Ancient Star Queen
snippet.description:
Blessings Star Family! 🌟
Channeled messaged I received April, 2017- "You hail from Ancient Star Kings and Queens. There aren't many of you left, but enough to start a revolution. Go find the others."

I’m a devotee & priestess of the Primordial Goddess, Divine Mother, who has been conflated throughout history via many names & forms. She is One, She is All:  Auset/Isis, Hathor, Hecate, Juno, Kali, Atabey, Mary, and more. My channel’s name comes from this message channeled from Her while in meditation and trance. 

I’m here to find the others. So if you connect my readings, I consider you brothers & sisters of the same Star Family Tribe.

✨ Channel readings are general & timeless. 
✨ My channel is directed at a mature audience: 18 +


🔮 FOR PERSONAL READINGS  &  MY HANDMADE JEWELRY
PLEASE VISIT MY ETSY SHOP:  
www.etsy.com/shop/AncientStarQueen 

Instagram: AncientStarQueen 
Twitter: @AncientStarQ
Other channel: LIFE, LOVE, and the UNIVERSE

✌🏽+💜
